        </a>
        <p class="text-sm mt-1" style="color:#94a3b8">Free IT security tutorials for network professionals.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCBxPV1V0majbAR5PNu2ACw/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          aria-label="YouTube"
